            "id": "http://xinghuohan.cn/2020/10/20/Linux/UbuntuFlameshot/",
            "url": "http://xinghuohan.cn/2020/10/20/Linux/UbuntuFlameshot/",
            "title": "Ubuntu截图工具",
            "date_published": "2020-10-20T07:16:03.159Z",
            "content_html": "<p>Linux 系统 Ubuntu 截图工具推荐使用</p>\n<a id=\"more\"></a>\n<h3 id=\"前言\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#前言\">#</a> 前言</h3>\n<p>Windows 上习惯了 QQ 的截图工具，本工具类似 QQ 截图工具功能，在习惯 QQ 截图的情况下可以很方便的使用。效果图：<img src=\"/img/image-20201020151914799.png\" alt=\"image-20201020151914799\" srcset=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%20300%20300'%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-src=\"/img/image-20201020151914799.png\" class=\"lozad post-image\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"安装过程\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#安装过程\">#</a> 安装过程</h3>\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><span class=\"line\">sudo apt-get install flameshot</span><br></pre>\n<h3 id=\"启动命令\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#启动命令\">#</a> 启动命令</h3>\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><span class=\"line\">flameshot gui</span><br></pre>\n<h3 id=\"设置快捷方式\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#设置快捷方式\">#</a> 设置快捷方式</h3>\n<p><img src=\"/img/image-20201020152205127.png\" alt=\"image-20201020152205127\" srcset=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%20300%20300'%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-src=\"/img/image-20201020152205127.png\" class=\"lozad post-image\"></p>\n<p>本机操作系统版本为 Ubuntu 20.04, 不同版本可能设置快捷键位置名称有些不同，可以自行根据系统版本设置</p>\n<p>具体设置</p>\n<p><img src=\"/img/image-20201020152406303.png\" alt=\"image-20201020152406303\" srcset=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%20300%20300'%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-src=\"/img/image-20201020152406303.png\" class=\"lozad post-image\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"软件设置\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#软件设置\">#</a> 软件设置</h3>\n<p><img src=\"/img/image-20201020152618648.png\" alt=\"image-20201020152618648\" srcset=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%20300%20300'%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-src=\"/img/image-20201020152618648.png\" class=\"lozad post-image\"></p>\n",
            "tags": [
                "Linux",
                "Ubuntu"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "http://xinghuohan.cn/2020/10/16/Linux/VmWarekernelModuleUpdater/",
            "url": "http://xinghuohan.cn/2020/10/16/Linux/VmWarekernelModuleUpdater/",
            "title": "Linux系统下VMware kernel Module Updater弹框，Install失败",
            "date_published": "2020-10-16T08:03:05.580Z",
            "content_html": "<p>Ubuntu 系统更新后，打开 VMware 提示需要更新安装，点击安装失败问题解决<a id=\"more\"></a></p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>提示框<img src=\"/img/image-20201016160643674.png\" alt=\"image-20201016160643674\" srcset=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%20300%20300'%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-src=\"/img/image-20201016160643674.png\" class=\"lozad post-image\"></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>安装失败<img src=\"/img/image-20201016160730834.png\" alt=\"image-20201016160730834\" srcset=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%20300%20300'%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-src=\"/img/image-20201016160730834.png\" class=\"lozad post-image\"></p>\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><span class=\"line\">--处理方法</span><br><span class=\"line\">--打开终端执行如下代码</span><br><span class=\"line\">VMWARE_VERSION=workstation-15.5.1</span><br><span class=\"line\">TMP_FOLDER=/tmp/patch-vmware</span><br><span class=\"line\">rm -fdr $TMP_FOLDER</span><br><span class=\"line\">mkdir -p $TMP_FOLDER</span><br><span class=\"line\">cd $TMP_FOLDER</span><br><span class=\"line\">git clone https://github.com/mkubecek/vmware-host-modules.git</span><br><span class=\"line\">cd $TMP_FOLDER/vmware-host-modules</span><br><span class=\"line\">git checkout $VMWARE_VERSION</span><br><span class=\"line\">git fetch</span><br><span class=\"line\">make</span><br><span class=\"line\">-- 执行如下代码时需要输入管理员密码，输入完成后执行当前代码，但是后续的代码会终止，需要手动拷贝未执行其余命令继续操作，全部命令执行完成后，VMware即可正常使用</span><br><span class=\"line\">sudo make install</span><br><span class=\"line\">sudo rm /usr/lib/vmware/lib/libz.so.1/libz.so.1</span><br><span class=\"line\">sudo ln -s /lib/x86_64-linux-gnu/libz.so.1</span><br><span class=\"line\">/usr/lib/vmware/lib/libz.so.1/libz.so.1</span><br><span class=\"line\">sudo /etc/init.d/vmware restart</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br></pre>\n</li>\n</ol>\n",
            "tags": [
                "VMware"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "http://xinghuohan.cn/2020/10/16/Linux/UbuntuAboutDesktop/",
            "url": "http://xinghuohan.cn/2020/10/16/Linux/UbuntuAboutDesktop/",
            "title": "Ubuntu桌面被删除后",
            "date_published": "2020-10-16T07:37:31.201Z",
            "content_html": "<p>Ubuntu 桌面被误删除，Ubuntu 在重启时会校验当前设置路径是否存在，不存在会默认设置一个路径，我 Ubuntu20.04 版本删除桌面文件夹被删除后，将桌面路径默认为根目录，导致桌面一下子出现了很多文件，为了恢复桌面的清爽，而进行如下操作。<a id=\"more\"></a></p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>终端打开自己根目录</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>进入隐藏文件夹 .config<img src=\"/img/image-20201016154927244.png\" alt=\"image-20201016154927244\" srcset=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%20300%20300'%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-src=\"/img/image-20201016154927244.png\" class=\"lozad post-image\"></p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n   <pre class=\"highlight\"><span class=\"line\">-- 查看当前目录下所有文件</span><br><span class=\"line\">ls -la</span><br></pre>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>\n<p>编辑文件 vim user-dirs.dirs <img src=\"/img/image-20201016155127768.png\" alt=\"image-20201016155127768\" srcset=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%20300%20300'%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-src=\"/img/image-20201016155127768.png\" class=\"lozad post-image\"></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>进行如下修改，此处修改的路径需要自己先行在对应路径创建文件夹，然后重启即可。<img src=\"/img/image-20201016155252812.png\" alt=\"image-20201016155252812\" srcset=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%20300%20300'%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-src=\"/img/image-20201016155252812.png\" class=\"lozad post-image\"></p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n",
            "tags": [
                "Ubuntu"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "http://xinghuohan.cn/2020/10/14/Linux/CommonCommands/",
            "url": "http://xinghuohan.cn/2020/10/14/Linux/CommonCommands/",
            "title": "Linux常用命令",
            "date_published": "2020-10-14T05:05:50.142Z",
            "content_html": "<p>Linux 系统常用基本命令</p>\n<a id=\"more\"></a>\n<h3 id=\"ack-待查询字符串\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#ack-待查询字符串\">#</a> ack  [待查询字符串]</h3>\n<p>搜索当前文件夹内所有文件中对应的字符（递归查询）</p>\n<h3 id=\"unar-待解压文件\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#unar-待解压文件\">#</a> unar  [待解压文件]</h3>\n<p>解压命令，可以解压 zip 文件，主要可以解决 windows 系统中的部分文件解压后乱码问题</p>\n",
            "tags": [
                "Linux",
                "Ubuntu",
                "CentOS"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "http://xinghuohan.cn/2020/09/09/Linux/Centos-staticIP/",
            "url": "http://xinghuohan.cn/2020/09/09/Linux/Centos-staticIP/",
            "title": "Centos设置静态ip",
            "date_published": "2020-09-09T14:23:46.572Z",
            "content_html": "<p>Centos 设置静态 IP</p>\n<p>Vmware workstation 中的 centos ip 地址会在没重启的情况下发生变化。 虚拟机的 IP 租约过期后，IP 就会自动重新分配，从而造成 IP 地址自行变化。</p>\n<p>为了应用方便，需要设置 centos 的固定 ip。 版本 centos7</p>\n<p>设置步骤 1.ifconfig 找到当前的 centos 的 ip</p>\n<p>2. 进入文件 vim /etc/sysconfig/network-scripts/ifcfg-ens33</p>\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><span class=\"line\">TYPE=Ethernet</span><br><span class=\"line\">PROXY_METHOD=none</span><br><span class=\"line\">BROWSER_ONLY=no</span><br><span class=\"line\">BOOTPROTO=static</span><br><span class=\"line\">DEFROUTE=yes</span><br><span class=\"line\">IPV4_FAILURE_FATAL=no</span><br><span class=\"line\">IPV6INIT=yes</span><br><span class=\"line\">IPV6_AUTOCONF=yes</span><br><span class=\"line\">IPV6_DEFROUTE=yes</span><br><span class=\"line\">IPV6_FAILURE_FATAL=no</span><br><span class=\"line\">IPV6_ADDR_GEN_MODE=stable-privacy</span><br><span class=\"line\">NAME=ens33</span><br><span class=\"line\">UUID=529b576d-4e86-4dd1-9446-43ab40dbfd27</span><br><span class=\"line\">DEVICE=ens33</span><br><span class=\"line\">ONBOOT=yes</span><br><span class=\"line\">IPADDR=192.168.88.88</span><br><span class=\"line\">NETMASK=255.255.255.0</span><br><span class=\"line\">GATEWAY=192.168.88.2</span><br><span class=\"line\">DNS1=192.168.88.2</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br></pre>\n<p>3. 重启网络服务 使用命令 systemctl restart network.service</p>\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><span class=\"line\">--关闭网络管理器NetwokManager</span><br><span class=\"line\">systemctl stop NetworkManager</span><br><span class=\"line\">systemctl disable NetworkManager</span><br><span class=\"line\">service network restart</span><br></pre>\n",
            "tags": [
                "Linux",
                "Centos"
            ]
        }
    ]
}